headline: Why The Current Bull Market Deserves Your Trust Against Popular Doubt
summary: Brian Belski, Chief Investment Strategist at BMO Capital Markets, calls the run that just pushed the S&P to 6,000 and the Dow to 44,000 a bull market no one believes in.
